{"tid":210682,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊/做過starbucks嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2017-04-21T06:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T11:01:31.000Z","uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c76c7595bc5a200506a394bdbd26495bd99242bc","tid":210682,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"考完DSE想見starbucks part time<br />\n由細到大都好鐘意沖咖啡所以應該會長做<br />\n有冇人知道見工個流程係點同埋有咩條件先請<br />\n因為好有興趣所以報過啲19工聯會嘅咖啡進階班<br />\n有證書唔知有冇幫助呢？<br />\n仲有遲啲會去考咖啡牌洗唔洗同佢講黎搏加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好想做呀求巴打絲打班班手<br />\n由低做起會比人鬧都唔緊<br />\n利申未出過黎做野/見工 性格頗算外向（唔靚仔但都唔算樣哀）"},{"pid":"6cf95071a5d786314f6a2d75ba516783531f7ce5","tid":210682,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:22:26.000Z","msg":"邊個比完負皮就走咁算點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc480919dbc467a218c9d18bc3abbbf0c5e115e8","tid":210682,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:23:52.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ae41d7fc5496089943888130f832d468929992","tid":210682,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:25:25.000Z","msg":"fuck比完負皮都屌番兩句先走啦"},{"pid":"d2a66a440162792e0ec975c938890a82391229c7","tid":210682,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6c0c92e87c1dbf842cf19efaf3eca854521186","tid":210682,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:30:11.000Z","msg":"成個連登冇人做starbucks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd336be70dbd5208473b6a2c07add49a41d5e3c","tid":210682,"uid":61830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"未做過starbucks<br />\n但真係出黎做野同你幻想既會差一大段距離<br />\n你幻想既係可以慢慢整一杯好味既咖啡比人飲而滿足<br />\n現實係一大推單等緊你出 根本無時間比你慢慢品味 忙同埋不斷重複既工作好快會磨滅你既鬥志<br />\n<br />\n利申：以前做水吧and廚房"},{"pid":"f486fc54ca09b9e6343e045fe586be6875ba22d7","tid":210682,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未做過starbucks<br />\n但真係出黎做野同你幻想既會差一大段距離<br />\n你幻想既係可以慢慢整一杯好味既咖啡比人飲而滿足<br />\n現實係一大推單等緊你出 根本無時間比你慢慢品味 忙同埋不斷重複既工作好快會磨滅你既鬥志<br />\n<br />\n利申：以前做水吧and廚房</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都係好想去試下<br />\n唔想做老麥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005227bc76f7bd1843a2cc594d099d4e48f5631c","tid":210682,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"又沉左"},{"pid":"5fee7a116f00791b283f0aa4f9ee08c63e0fa79e","tid":210682,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bd925cdefa3346f492ed85facc4b437495151a","tid":210682,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"starbucks係禁制唔係學沖咖啡<br />\n<br />\n想學沖咖啡去mc cafe同pacific coffee會好啲<br />\n<br />\n利申︰聽人講過"},{"pid":"a8bc556528294b150ee3c8c0774790bf64aab83f","tid":210682,"uid":33107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:37:48.000Z","msg":"見工流程同你傾下計吹下水既姐，問下你食物既簡單英文，但對咖啡行業好有熱誠既話唔建議你做星仔啦，基本上係學企pastry先，學打till再到埋吧沖咖啡，但做落你就知屎坑有舊屎都要你去執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沖咖啡方面要快爲主啦，做起上黎邊有時間同心機去整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e141c5c311454